# RFSoC4x2 AWG Docs

Documentation for the RFSoC4x2 AWG implementation:
https://github.com/selfoluap/RFSoC4x2-AWG

Published docs:
https://rfsoc4x2-awg-docs.readthedocs.io/en/latest/

This site uses MkDocs.

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/selfoluap/RFSoC4x2-AWG-docs
```

Create a virtual environment and install MkDocs:

```bash
python3 -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate
pip install mkdocs
```

Serve the documentation locally:

```bash
cd docs
mkdocs serve --live-reload
```

Open http://localhost:8000/RFSoC4x2-AWG/ in your browser.
